[
  {
    "startTime": 0.3,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's Frozen, now available on Blue-Ray and DVD."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 8.6,
    "text": "Princess Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.6,
    "endTime": 9.4,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.4,
    "endTime": 10.4,
    "text": "Princess Anna?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.4,
    "endTime": 11.4,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.4,
    "endTime": 12.8,
    "text": "Sorry to wake you, ma'am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.8,
    "endTime": 21.18,
    "text": "No, no, no, no, you didn't, I've been up for hours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.1,
    "endTime": 22.26,
    "text": "Who is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.26,
    "endTime": 24.090000000000003,
    "text": "Still me, ma'am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.09,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "The gates will open soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 27.2,
    "text": "Time to get ready."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.2,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.24,
    "text": "Ready for what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.24,
    "endTime": 32.699999999999996,
    "text": "Your sister's coronation, ma'am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.7,
    "endTime": 38.400000000000006,
    "text": "My sister's corn-oration."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.4,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "It's Coronation Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 42.1,
    "text": "The Duke of Weasel Town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.1,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Weselton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 45.7,
    "text": "Duke of Weselton, Your Majesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.7,
    "endTime": 52.156000000000006,
    "text": "As your closest partner in trade, it seems only fitting that I offer you your first dance as Queen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.4,
    "endTime": 56.929,
    "text": "Jump!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.01,
    "endTime": 60.12,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.12,
    "endTime": 61.169999999999995,
    "text": "Only I don't dance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.25,
    "endTime": 64.366,
    "text": "But my sister does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.366,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Oh, lucky you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Oh, I don't think -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 69.48,
    "text": "If you swoon, let me know, I'll catch you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.48,
    "endTime": 70.60000000000001,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.6,
    "endTime": 74.69999999999999,
    "text": "Like an agile peacock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.7,
    "endTime": 77.60000000000001,
    "text": "Speaking of, so great to have the gates open."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.6,
    "endTime": 80.1,
    "text": "Why did they shut them in the first place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.1,
    "endTime": 84.01599999999999,
    "text": "Do you know the reason? Hmm? - No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.016,
    "endTime": 86.19000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, alright, hang on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.19,
    "endTime": 95.7,
    "text": "They don't call me the Little Dipper for nothing, oh ho, like a chicken with the face of a monkey. I fly!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.7,
    "endTime": 106.10000000000001,
    "text": "Of course, none of it would've happened if she just told me her secret. She's a stinker."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.1,
    "endTime": 108.21,
    "text": "Oh, no, no, no, no, come back!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.21,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "No, no, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 114.901,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.08,
    "endTime": 119.6,
    "text": "Snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.6,
    "endTime": 121.32,
    "text": "It had to be snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.32,
    "endTime": 131.1,
    "text": "She couldn't have had tropical magic that covered the fjords in white sand and warm fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 147.4,
    "text": "Cold, cold, cold, cold -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.4,
    "endTime": 153.48000000000002,
    "text": "Big summer blowout, half off swimming suits, clogs and a sun balm of my own invention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.48,
    "endTime": 155.16,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.16,
    "endTime": 156.7,
    "text": "Oh, great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.7,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "For now, um, how about boots, winter boots and dresses?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "That would be in our winter department."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 169.7,
    "text": "Oh, um, I was just wondering."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.8,
    "endTime": 175.60000000000002,
    "text": "Has another young woman, the Queen, perhaps, I don't know, passed through here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.6,
    "endTime": 185.7,
    "text": "Only one crazy enough to be out in this storm is you, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.7,
    "endTime": 187.2,
    "text": "You and this fellow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.29,
    "endTime": 191.011,
    "text": "Whoo hoo, big summer blow out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.4,
    "endTime": 197.70000000000002,
    "text": "- Carrot. - Hm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.7,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "Behind you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 202.47,
    "text": "Oh, right, excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.47,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "Whoa, a real howler in July, yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 207.4,
    "text": "Wherever could it be coming from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.4,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "The North Mountain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 211.7,
    "text": "The North Mountain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.7,
    "endTime": 212.79999999999998,
    "text": "That'll be $40."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.8,
    "endTime": 215.0,
    "text": "$40? No, $10."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "Oh dear, that's no good. See, this is from our winter stock where supply and demand have a big problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 222.12,
    "text": "You wanna talk about a supply and demand problem?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.12,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "I sell ice for a living."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "Ooh, that's a rough business to be in right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 229.6,
    "text": "I mean, that is really, that's unfortunate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.6,
    "endTime": 233.28,
    "text": "Still $40, but I will throw in a visit to oaken sauna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.1,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Whoo hoo, hi, family! - Whoo hoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 239.0,
    "text": "Ten's all I got."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.0,
    "endTime": 240.03,
    "text": "Help me out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.03,
    "endTime": 242.7,
    "text": "Okay. Ten will get you this, and no more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.7,
    "endTime": 243.7,
    "text": "Okay, just tell me one thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.7,
    "endTime": 248.7,
    "text": "What was happening on the North Mountain? Did it seem magical?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.7,
    "endTime": 256.09999999999997,
    "text": "Yes. Now back up while I deal with this crook here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.1,
    "endTime": 258.70000000000005,
    "text": "What did you call me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.7,
    "endTime": 261.4,
    "text": "Okay, okay, I'm out, oww -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.4,
    "endTime": 264.5,
    "text": "Bye bye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.5,
    "endTime": 267.0,
    "text": "Hang on, we like to go fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.0,
    "endTime": 267.9,
    "text": "I like fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.0,
    "endTime": 270.0,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. Get your feet down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.0,
    "endTime": 271.23,
    "text": "This is fresh lacquer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.23,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "Seriously, were you raised in a barn?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 278.6,
    "text": "Ooh, no, I was raised in a castle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.6,
    "endTime": 282.18,
    "text": "So tell me, what made the queen go all ice crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.18,
    "endTime": 285.3,
    "text": "Oh, well, it was all my fault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.3,
    "endTime": 290.04,
    "text": "I got engaged, but then she freaked out because I'd only just met him, you know, that day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.04,
    "endTime": 292.0,
    "text": "And she said she wouldn't bless the marriage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.2,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "Wait, you got engaged to someone you just met that day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 296.3,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.3,
    "endTime": 301.5,
    "text": "Anyway, I got mad and so she got mad and then she tried to walk away and I grabbed her gloves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.5,
    "endTime": 301.8,
    "text": "Hang on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 307.0,
    "text": "You mean to tell me you got engaged to someone you just met that day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.0,
    "endTime": 308.3,
    "text": "Yes, pay attention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.3,
    "endTime": 312.0,
    "text": "But the thing is, she wore the gloves all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.0,
    "endTime": 314.04,
    "text": "So I just thought maybe she has a thing about dirt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.04,
    "endTime": 318.3,
    "text": "Didn't your parents ever warn you about strangers?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.3,
    "endTime": 320.0,
    "text": "Yes, they did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.0,
    "endTime": 322.4,
    "text": "But Hans is not a stranger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.4,
    "endTime": 325.09999999999997,
    "text": "Oh yeah. What's his last name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.1,
    "endTime": 327.0,
    "text": "Of the Southern Isles?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.0,
    "endTime": 327.7,
    "text": "What's his favorite food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.7,
    "endTime": 328.59999999999997,
    "text": "Sandwiches."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.6,
    "endTime": 329.0,
    "text": "Best friend's name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.0,
    "endTime": 329.8,
    "text": "Probably John."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.8,
    "endTime": 330.8,
    "text": "Eye color? - Dreamy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.8,
    "endTime": 331.1,
    "text": "Foot size?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.1,
    "endTime": 332.5,
    "text": "Foot size doesn't matter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.5,
    "endTime": 334.0,
    "text": "Have you had a meal with him yet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.0,
    "endTime": 335.3,
    "text": "What if you hate the way he eats?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.3,
    "endTime": 336.7,
    "text": "What if you hate the way he picks his nose?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.7,
    "endTime": 338.28,
    "text": "Picks his nose?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.28,
    "endTime": 339.45,
    "text": "And eats it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.45,
    "endTime": 343.0,
    "text": "Excuse me, sir. He is a prince."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.0,
    "endTime": 345.2,
    "text": "All men do it. - Ew."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.2,
    "endTime": 350.0,
    "text": "I never knew winter could be so beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.0,
    "endTime": 353.43,
    "text": "Yeah, it really is beautiful, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.43,
    "endTime": 355.0,
    "text": "But it's so white."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.0,
    "endTime": 357.12,
    "text": "You know, have a little color."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.12,
    "endTime": 362.37,
    "text": "I'm thinking like maybe some crimson, chartreuse, how about yellow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.37,
    "endTime": 363.39,
    "text": "No, not yellow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.39,
    "endTime": 369.59999999999997,
    "text": "Yellow and snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.6,
    "endTime": 371.40000000000003,
    "text": "Am I right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.4,
    "endTime": 373.0,
    "text": "Hi. - You're creepy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.0,
    "endTime": 373.8,
    "text": "- Whoa. - I don't want it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.8,
    "endTime": 375.0,
    "text": "Whoa, back at you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.0,
    "endTime": 377.0,
    "text": "Please don't drop me. You know I'm just a head."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.0,
    "endTime": 378.0,
    "text": "All right, we got off to a bad start."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.1,
    "endTime": 383.5,
    "text": "Ew, ew, the body."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.5,
    "endTime": 385.2,
    "text": "Wait, what am I looking at right now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.1,
    "endTime": 387.42100000000005,
    "text": "Why are you hanging off the earth like a bat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.421,
    "endTime": 389.59999999999997,
    "text": "All right, wait one second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.6,
    "endTime": 393.18,
    "text": "Oh, oh. Oh, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.18,
    "endTime": 393.7,
    "text": "You're welcome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.7,
    "endTime": 396.59999999999997,
    "text": "Now I'm perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.6,
    "endTime": 398.0,
    "text": "Well, almost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.0,
    "endTime": 400.0,
    "text": "It was like my whole life got turned upside down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.0,
    "endTime": 402.48,
    "text": "Whoo! - I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.48,
    "endTime": 405.0,
    "text": "- Head rush. - Are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.0,
    "endTime": 407.37,
    "text": "Are you kidding me? I am wonderful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.37,
    "endTime": 409.0,
    "text": "I've always wanted a nose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.0,
    "endTime": 412.0,
    "text": "It's so cute. It's like a little baby unicorn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.3,
    "endTime": 414.0,
    "text": "What, hey, whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.0,
    "endTime": 417.666,
    "text": "Oh, I love it even more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.3,
    "endTime": 420.0,
    "text": "All right, let's start this thing over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.0,
    "endTime": 424.6,
    "text": "Hi everyone. I'm Olaf and I like warm hugs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.6,
    "endTime": 428.8,
    "text": "Olaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.8,
    "endTime": 432.027,
    "text": "That's right. Olaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.027,
    "endTime": 435.0,
    "text": "And you are -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.0,
    "endTime": 437.0,
    "text": "Oh, I'm Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.0,
    "endTime": 439.17,
    "text": "And who's the funky looking donkey over there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.17,
    "endTime": 440.13,
    "text": "That's Sven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.13,
    "endTime": 442.7,
    "text": "Uh huh, and who's the reindeer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.7,
    "endTime": 443.4,
    "text": "Sven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.4,
    "endTime": 447.5,
    "text": "Oh, they're both, oh, okay. Make things easier for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.5,
    "endTime": 449.31,
    "text": "Oh, look at him trying to kiss my nose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.31,
    "endTime": 451.0,
    "text": "I like you too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.0,
    "endTime": 453.03,
    "text": "Olaf, did Elsa build you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.03,
    "endTime": 454.14,
    "text": "Yeah, why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.14,
    "endTime": 454.9,
    "text": "Do you know where she is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.9,
    "endTime": 456.4,
    "text": "Fascinating. - Yeah, why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.4,
    "endTime": 458.59999999999997,
    "text": "Do you think you could show us the way? - Yeah, why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.6,
    "endTime": 463.0,
    "text": "How does this work? Ow. - Stop it Sven. Try and focus here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.0,
    "endTime": 464.6,
    "text": "Yeah, why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.6,
    "endTime": 467.0,
    "text": "Meet my family?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.0,
    "endTime": 468.39,
    "text": "Hey guys!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.39,
    "endTime": 470.0,
    "text": "They're rocks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.0,
    "endTime": 472.29,
    "text": "You are a sight for sore eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.29,
    "endTime": 475.3,
    "text": "He's cra-zy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.3,
    "endTime": 478.0,
    "text": "Rocko's looking sharp as usual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.0,
    "endTime": 481.0,
    "text": "Hey, whoa, I don't even recognize you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.0,
    "endTime": 482.0,
    "text": "You lost so much weight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.0,
    "endTime": 485.0,
    "text": "I'll distract him while you run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.0,
    "endTime": 489.6,
    "text": "Hi Sven's family. It's nice to meet you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.6,
    "endTime": 492.09000000000003,
    "text": "Because I love you, Anna, I insist you run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.09,
    "endTime": 495.47999999999996,
    "text": "I understand you're love experts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.48,
    "endTime": 498.88300000000004,
    "text": "Whoo, why aren't you running?"
  }
]